1. A lithium battery SOH detection method of BMS is characterized in that: comprises the following steps
 Firstly, applying specific frequency excitation by scanning by utilizing the frequency domain response characteristic of the alternating small signal of the lithium battery, and respectively detecting the voltage response and the current response of the alternating small signal of the lithium battery under the specific frequency;
 secondly, performing superposition calculation with the excitation signal to obtain alternating current small signal impedance data of the lithium battery at the frequency;
 thirdly, fitting an alternating current small signal impedance Nyquist diagram of the battery in a section of frequency by analyzing impedance data under multiple groups of frequencies;
